These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, punk, hip-hop, funk
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, british, chinese, canadian
4 different pets are kept: mouse, goldfish, pony, goat
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, car, airplane, subway
 1. the japanese is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
 2. the owner of the pony is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 3. the fan of techno is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the owner of the goat is the british##1
 5. the person driving the van is somewhere to the left of the person driving the airplane##5
 6. the japanese is somewhere to the left of the person driving the car##5
 7. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left##1
 8. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the left of the british##5
 9. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the chinese##3
10. the owner of the goat is somewhere between the person driving the van and the fan of techno##7
11. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
12. the canadian is somewhere to the right of the person driving the subway##5
13. the person driving the subway is the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | funk    | punk | hip-hop    | techno   |
| Nationality   | japanese | chinese | british | canadian |
| Pet           | goldfish       | pony   | goat  | mouse     |
| Transport     | van      | airplane   | subway    | car    |

