.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-2::.
There 4 different types of food: pepper, zucchini, avocado, pineapple
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, zombie, superhero, satire
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, dutch, colombian, malaysian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, cycling, handball, swimming
 1. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cycling##5
 2. the colombian is somewhere to the right of the malaysian##5
 3. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating pineapple##5
 4. the person who's sport is handball is the polish##1
 5. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the colombian##3
 6. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the person eating avocado##5
 7. the person eating pineapple is somewhere between the person who's sport is cycling and the polish##7
 8. the person eating pepper is in an odd position##4
 9. the person eating pepper is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cycling##5
10. the person watching satire movies is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is cricket##5
11. the dutch is the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |       3       |     4      |
| Food          | pepper   | avocado       | pineapple    | zucchini      |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | satire | zombie         | superhero   |
| Nationality   | malaysian   | polish  | dutch       | colombian |
| Sport         | cricket      | handball  | swimming | cycling |

