 2. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the fisherman and the person watching sports movies##7
 3. the accountant is the italian##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the software-developer##3
 5. the british is on the left or right of the person watching spy movies##3
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of the person watching disaster movies##5
 7. the pilot is not the person watching musical movies##6
 8. the person watching sports movies is not the software-developer##6
 9. the fisherman is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
10. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
11. the accountant is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3
12. the mexican is the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3     |        4        |
