 7. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the freelancer##1
 8. the coach is somewhere between the person who's hobby is fishing and the person who's hobby is woodworking##7
 9. the coach is the person watching horror movies##1
10. the person drinking water is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
11. the videographer is not the person watching horror movies##6

.:: Answer ::.
