.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, 7up, almond-milk, cola
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, papaya, radish, spinach
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, rock-climbing, singing, video-games
4 different pets are kept: ferret, bird, chinchilla, turtle
 1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
 2. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the person eating pomegranate##5
 3. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the owner of the turtle and the owner of the chinchilla##2
 4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
 5. the person eating papaya is not the owner of the bird##6
 6. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere to the left of the person eating radish##5
 7. the person drinking cola is somewhere between the person drinking juice and the person eating spinach##7
 8. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the left of the owner of the chinchilla##5
 9. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
10. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
11. the person drinking juice is the person eating radish##1
12. the person eating radish is not the owner of the chinchilla##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up   | cola     | almond-milk   | juice |
| Food       | spinach   | pomegranate | papaya | radish    |
| Hobby      | singing | video-games | cooking   | rock-climbing  |
| Pet        | turtle | ferret     | chinchilla   | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda, lemonade, milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, video-games, writing, photography
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, pilot, videographer, accountant
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, ambient, house, gospel
 1. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5
 2. the fan of punk is between the person who's hobby is writing and the coach##2
 3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
 4. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1
 5. the accountant is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the fan of ambient is not the videographer##6
 7. the videographer is somewhere between the person who's hobby is photography and the person who's hobby is card-games##7
 8. the fan of punk is not the person who's hobby is card-games##6
 9. the accountant is not the person who's hobby is photography##6
10. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
11. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
12. the person who's hobby is writing is not the person drinking mirinda##6
13. the videographer is on the left of the accountant##1
14. the coach is on the left or right of the fan of punk##3
15. the pilot is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3        |      4      |
| Beverage      | mirinda      | almond-milk        | milk          | lemonade    |
| Hobby         | photography | video-games    | writing          | card-games |
| Job           | coach  | pilot   | videographer | accountant      |
| Music-Genre   | gospel       | punk | house          | ambient        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, writing, gardening, sudoku
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, nurse, librarian, writer
4 different pets are kept: ferret, frog, cat, rat
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, basketball, biathlon, climbing
 1. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##5
 2. the librarian is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 3. the person who's sport is basketball is the owner of the rat##1
 4. the owner of the cat is between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person who's hobby is writing##2
 5. the software-developer is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is writing##5
 6. the owner of the ferret is somewhere between the librarian and the person who's hobby is collecting##7
 7. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the left of the nurse##5
 8. the owner of the ferret is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 9. the nurse is somewhere to the left of the software-developer##5
10. the owner of the frog is on the far right##1
11. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an even position##4
12. the software-developer is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is writing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Hobby   | sudoku      | gardening     | writing   | collecting    |
| Job     | writer | librarian   | nurse | software-developer |
| Pet     | rat        | cat     | ferret  | frog      |
| Sport   | basketball       | climbing | lacrosse   | biathlon    |

 